The,GSMA,is,an,association,of,mobile,operators,worldwide,Representing,more,than,mobile,operators,in,more,than,countries,the,GSMA,supports,the,standardizing,deployment,and,promotion,of,the,GSM,mobile,telephone,system,The,GSMA,also,produces,industry,leading,events,such,as,the,Mobile,World,Congress,and,Mobile,Asia,Expo,The,GSMA,OneAPI,is,a,set,of,APIs,that,expose,network,capabilities,over,HTTP,The,OneAPI,MMS,SMS,interface,allows,a,Web,application,to,send,and,receive,MMS,and,SMS,messages,It,uses,both,REST,and,SOAP,protocola,with,responses,in,XML,and,JSON